&lt;/h3>&lt;p>Afterwards you can upgrade the theme with the following command:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># Update theme manually&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">hugo mod get -u github.com/hugo-fixit/FixIt@latest
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">hugo mod tidy&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
